          <h3>About Us</h3>
          <p>Sheltr aims to provide a single database of resources available to individuals affected by homelessness and near homelessness.  This database will be utilized via computer, smart phone, and SMS to locate resources that are relevant geographically and demographically. The target audience is mainly case managers, social workers, and organizations assisting the homeless population, but it is also catered to those affected by homelessness, and citizens with interest in assisting homeless fellow citizens.</p>
